{
  "text": "I see what you're saying is these naive Confederation entities have had the same thing happen to them in the past, so they were doing the same thing for the Atlantic entities. Is this correct? I am wrong. This is correct. We remind you that we are one of the naive members of that confederation. It is our duty as well as honor to continue with your peoples, therefore, until all traces of the distortions of our teach learnings have been embraced by their opposite distortions and balance achieved.",
